About the codefest:

Working on twitter data set that contain tweets about customer review on different companies and products. 
Job was to find the tweets which showed a negatives sentiment towards such companies or product.

Analysis is done in different parts:
Details given below:

1) Data Preprocessing: Which include data cleaning, removal of noise tec. 
2) Feature Extraction: TF-IDF method for sparse vector representation.
3) Data modeling: machine learning algorithm are used to classify output. 

Note: more updates are coming for this project ....
